735
01:13:05,488 --> 01:13:08,688
Borough 13.
How could I forget.

736
01:13:09,688 --> 01:13:11,088
The rest you can do.

737
01:13:11,088 --> 01:13:13,528
Are you crazy?
Do you want to blow up the middle of Paris?

738
01:13:13,528 --> 01:13:15,968
I don't get it.
Isn't this the code to disarm the bomb?

739
01:13:16,088 --> 01:13:18,088
I hope it's not a code
to arm it?

740
01:13:18,088 --> 01:13:21,688
- Enough of these charades! You know full well!
- No I don't. Explain it to me.

741
