745
01:13:34,648 --> 01:13:37,448
- No, no don't do it.
- But you wanna clean up?

746
01:13:37,448 --> 01:13:40,688
- We'll all die.
- You should of thought of that when you built it.

747
01:13:40,688 --> 01:13:41,448
No!

748
01:13:54,688 --> 01:13:57,848
You believed me? That I'd blow
everything up, including ourselves?

749
01:13:58,688 --> 01:14:00,848
